title: Pharrell and The Yessirs - Out of My Mind 320kbps
description:
This album is a remix of Pharrell\&#039;s solo debut, In My Mind, which is produced by The Roots\&#039; drummer, ?uestlove and keyboardist James Poyser.

Enjoy!
